BMF: I got a chance to meet/work with the Queen @therealmoworldwide, not only did I meet her but we were trailer buddies. My emotions are all over the place about this post 😅 because I genuinely wanted to see her back on my screen because I enjoy her work!! Full circle moment, I’m on set with her a year later, being her trailer buddy made me think about how close I am to greatness! I like to take certain things as a sign of where I will be in the near future, it’s only a matter of time!! Thank you so much for the opportunity @bmfstarz 🙏🏽🖤 #Manfestation
Self Care: A little something I do to stay happy!! 😌💆🏽‍♂️
🇩🇴: Dominican Papi 😏🌊😜🛥️
She said she never had breakfast on a yacht before…..😏😌🍉🌊

2023: He’s Authentic, Genuine, Respectful, Loving, Caring, Down to Earth, Always observing/listening to learn, Full of Joy, Focus on Positivity and Talk to God EVERYDAY!! Yet, he’s not perfect, make/made mistakes, not always right, don’t know everything, can get emotional and don’t always have it together…..We’re always gonna be a working progress to become the best version of ourselves!! Just let that be your #1 focus! 🫡

The Love of Family: I really can’t believe I just seen my niece in heels 😖🥹 We sent her off to graduation yesterday and she was so beautiful! 🥹😍 I really enjoyed myself and I thank god for that experience! 🙏🏽……Family is my life and everything else comes second as far as what's important to me. 🖤 I’m so much of a family man and use to be so close with my family before I started this journey that’s been keeping me away from my family most of the time only to grind and manifest my dreams for something much greater than me. Some ppl wouldn’t understand how much it hurts to choose between seeing my family or manifesting my dreams but God always put me in a position to make up for it! I’m SO GRATEFUL that my nieces and nephews still remember my heart, energy and love for them even though I’m not there physically most of the time. Thank you God once again and Londyn, Congratulations on going to high school 😖 OMG I can’t believe I just said that 😅 She’s growing up on me but I love you with all my heart my Londy Lon! 🖤😘
6.22.23 🎈Because GOD!!

Today is a VERY special day!! Season 2 of “The Black Hamptons” is FINALLY BACK & Alongside that it’s my Queen, My Heart, My Lovely Mother’s Birthday!!! 😅🥹🙌🏽 Now how ironic is it that you get to have your show premiere on your mother’s birthday?! which is one of her favorite shows btw 😁 Y’all have been waiting so go catch the first episode and also tell my mom “HAPPY BIRTHDAY!” 😁😅😍🤗🖤 @blackhamptonsbet @betplus

To know that we’ll all be gone one day is mind blowing!!! 🥹 That’s why I live life TO THE FULLEST & MIND MY BUSINESS, treat ppl with LOVE & RESPECT while I’m here!!! Oh yea, Ep. 3 of the “Black Hamptons” is out btw! 🤭
She’s MY WOMAN LIKE I SAID‼️ World Champ or not, Ima fight for mine‼️🤬 Ep. 4 out now!! Oh DETROIT, I’m having a “Watch Party” next Thursday (12/28) 😏 LINK IN BIO

DETROIT: I’m FINALLY coming home!! 😅 And I want y’all to come celebratewith me so if you really support me and you will be in town, Click the “LINK IN BIO” and come turn up with me!! See y’all there!! 😏 Champagne Toast at 9:55pm 🥂

Fun fact: When I booked A Wesley Christmas I didn’t tell anyone. Then Mike calls me and says he’s in this movie too! And I was like NO WAY! And he was like I’m playing your love interest!!! And we started cracking up! We always thought it was a possibility to play opposites but at the time it seemed so future tense lol. Well surprise!! Not only were we in the same movie but we’re a couple!! lol absolutely hilarious! And we had a blast!! We are crazzzyyy! Love you so much lol please don’t ever stop being the biggest ball of sunshine @_mikemerrill_ !!! Merry christmas!! Say it back 💙🎄 #merrychristmas #wesleychristmaswedding
🚨 DETROIT: We’re going UP Thursday in our All Black for the “Black Hamptons Watch Party”!! Champagne Toast 🥂 at 9:55pm!! See y’all there!! 😁 (LINK IN BIO)
Have y’all ever been stuck between loving two ppl at the same time?! 🥹 Yea, that shit hurt don’t it?! 😫🖤 Martin & Karrin is BACK!! 😅🙌🏽 Ep. 5 OUT NOW!! WATCH PARTY TONIGHT!! 😁

Last Day of 2023: I ended this year off surrounded by genuine, authentic, real love!! 🥹 Thursday, everyone came out to celebrate your boy and watch an episode of “Black Hamptons” with me! I feel so RECHARGED and ready for the New Year, that City love hits different!! 🤭😂 Then I had my family there too!! 🖤 I wouldn’t have changed this for the world!! To every single person that follows me on my journey and show me love, I love every single one of you and if no one have told you, I’m saying it now on the last day of 2023 and pray you have a beautiful year in 2024!! 🙏🏽🖤🥂
Mama’s Boy of the Year!! 😌 The Handsome Snitch 🙃 Karin’s Man Again 😍 Ep. 6 had y’all HOT 😂 I’m ready for all the smoke, come on LET’S TALK ABOUT IT!! 😌

2024: You’re always right where you suppose to be!! That’s the word of the year from GOD, I’m thankful for Awarness!! 🙏🏽 “The Book of Clarence” was PHENOMENAL, everyone played their parts VERY WELL and I also learned some things that I didn’t know so please go support this film and see us in this light for ONCE!! ✊🏽💯
